---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Disclaimer from '../components/Disclaimer.astro';
---

<PageLayout
	title="About This Blog"
	description="A modern personal blog platform built with Astro. Learn more about the features and capabilities."
>
	<!-- Hero Image - Full width, properly contained -->
	<div class="mb-8 md:mb-12 animate-fade-up">
		<img 
			src="/images/default.avif" 
			alt="A modern blog platform showcasing clean design and powerful features" 
			class="w-full h-auto object-cover rounded-lg shadow-lg"
			loading="eager"
		/>
	</div>

	<div class="space-y-4 md:space-y-6 prose prose-lg max-w-none">
		<p class="animate-fade-up animate-fade-up-delay-1">
			Welcome to a modern, feature-rich personal blog platform.
		</p>

		<p class="animate-fade-up animate-fade-up-delay-2">
			This blog is built with Astro, a modern static site generator that delivers exceptional performance and developer experience. It's designed to be easily customizable, allowing writers, thinkers, and creators to share their thoughts with the world.
		</p>

		<p class="animate-fade-up animate-fade-up-delay-3">
			The platform features advanced reading systems, multilingual support, and a clean, responsive design that works beautifully on all devices.
		</p>

		<p class="animate-fade-up animate-fade-up-delay-4">
			This blog platform includes the following features:
		</p>

		<ul class="animate-fade-up animate-fade-up-delay-5">
			<li><strong>Art & Expression</strong> 🎵 — creative content, aesthetic exploration, and artistic expression</li>
			<li><strong>Culture</strong> 🌍 — social norms, collective behavior, and cultural insights</li>
			<li><strong>DIY & Creation</strong> 🛠️ — physical builds, handmade goods, and creative projects</li>
			<li><strong>Personal Growth</strong> 🧘🏽‍♂️ — inner development, self-improvement, and personal transformation</li>
			<li><strong>Learning Projects</strong> 📚 — documentation of skills and knowledge acquisition</li>
			<li><strong>Metaspace</strong> 🌀 — reflections on the journey itself and meta-thinking</li>
			<li><strong>Family & Relationships</strong> 👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 — family dynamics, relationships, and personal connections</li>
			<li><strong>Society & Culture</strong> ⚖️ — social structures, cultural dynamics, and collective insights</li>
			<li><strong>Psychology</strong> 🧠 — human behavior, mental processes, and psychological insights</li>
			<li><strong>Systems & Strategy</strong> 💻 — technical systems, organizational design, and strategic thinking</li>
		</ul>

		<h2 class="animate-fade-up animate-fade-up-delay-6">🚀 Getting Started</h2>

		<p class="animate-fade-up animate-fade-up-delay-7">
			To use this blog platform for your own content:
		</p>

		<ol class="animate-fade-up animate-fade-up-delay-7">
			<li>Fork or clone this repository</li>
			<li>Update the configuration in <code>src/consts.ts</code></li>
			<li>Replace the sample content with your own writings</li>
			<li>Customize the categories and navigation to match your topics</li>
			<li>Deploy to your preferred hosting platform</li>
		</ol>

		<h2 class="animate-fade-up animate-fade-up-delay-8">🔧 Technical Features</h2>

		<p class="animate-fade-up animate-fade-up-delay-8">
			This platform includes several powerful tools for content creators:
		</p>

		<ul class="animate-fade-up animate-fade-up-delay-8">
			<li>📊 <a href="/brain-science/" class="text-[rgb(var(--color-accent))] hover:underline">Writing Analytics</a> — Analyze your writing patterns and content evolution</li>
			<li>🏷️ <a href="/tag-management" class="text-[rgb(var(--color-accent))] hover:underline">Tag Management</a> — Organize and categorize your content effectively</li>
			<li>🗺️ <a href="/guided-path" class="text-[rgb(var(--color-accent))] hover:underline">Guided Path</a> — Create curated reading experiences for your audience</li>
			<li>💬 <a href="/api/" class="text-[rgb(var(--color-accent))] hover:underline">Public API</a> — Access your content programmatically</li>
		</ul>

		<div class="card-alt p-6 border-l-4 border-[rgb(var(--color-primary))] animate-fade-up animate-fade-up-delay-8" role="complementary" aria-label="Disclaimer">
			<div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
				<span class="text-xl" aria-hidden="true">🌟</span>
				<span class="font-semibold">Platform Disclaimer</span>
			</div>
			<p class="text-body-muted m-0">This blog platform is designed for personal use and content sharing. The content shared here represents personal opinions and experiences. This blog is for informational and entertainment purposes only.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</PageLayout>
